#: ../../H/high-bit.rst:15
msgid ""
"[common] By extension, the most significant part of something other than a "
"data byte: \"Spare me the whole :ref:`saga`\\, just give me the high bit.\" "
"See also :ref:`meta-bit`\\, :ref:`dread-high-bit-disease`\\, and compare the"
" mainstream slang bottom line."
msgstr ""
"[一般的]拡張して、データバイト以外の何かの最も重要な部分。「全部の\\ :ref:`saga`\\ は勘弁してくれ、high bitだけくれ」。\\ "
":ref:`meta-bit`\\ 、\\ :ref:`dread-high-bit-disease`\\ も参照。また主流スラングのbottom "
"lineと比較せよ。"
